Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The most recent case of European foulbrood in Norway was reported in June 2018. The case was located in the same area (Agder Department, Aust-Agder County) where the current case was detected. The event was resolved on February 2019. The event summary and map are available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=27060. - Mod.CRD

